---
layout: base.njk
title: The News We Skip
---

<style>
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: clamp(1.35rem,5vw,1.75rem); font-weight:700; color:#78350f; margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
  .page-header p  { font-size:0.9rem; color:#b45309; max-width:640px; line-height:1.6; }

  .lang-tabs { display:flex; gap:0.4rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .lang-tab {
    padding:0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius:99px; font-size:0.8rem;
    font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; border:none;
    background:#fef3c7; color:#92400e; transition:background 0.15s;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; min-height:36px;
  }
  .lang-tab.active { background:#facc15; color:#78350f; }

  .stat-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr)); gap:1rem; margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .stat-card { background:#fff; border:2px solid #fde047; border-radius:1rem; padding:1.25rem 1rem; text-align:center; }
  .stat-num  { font-size:2rem; font-weight:700; color:#78350f; }
  .stat-lbl  { font-size:0.75rem; color:#b45309; margin-top:0.25rem; }

  .rejection-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.75rem; }
  .rejection-card {
    background:#fff7ed; border:1.5px solid #fde68a; border-radius:0.75rem;
    padding:0.9rem 1.1rem;
  }
  .rejection-title { font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:600; color:#78350f; line-height:1.4; }
  .rejection-meta  { font-size:0.75rem; color:#b45309; margin-top:0.25rem; display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .rejection-reason { font-size:0.8rem; color:#b45309; margin-top:0.4rem; font-style:italic; }
  .rejection-reason::before { content:"✗ "; color:#ef4444; }

  .empty { color:#b45309; font-size:0.9rem; }
  .updated { font-size:0.75rem; color:#d97706; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
</style>

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>
    <span class="t-en">The News We Skip 🚫</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Het nieuws dat we overslaan 🚫</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Les nouvelles que nous ignorons 🚫</span>
  </h1>
  <p>
    <span class="t-en">Every time we scan news sources, our AI reads the headline and filters out stories that are negative, anxiety-inducing, or just plain gloomy. This page shows what gets left behind — a small illustration of how skewed towards the negative most news coverage tends to be.</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Elke keer dat we nieuwsbronnen scannen, leest onze AI de kop en filtert verhalen die negatief, angstaanjagend of gewoon somber zijn. Deze pagina toont wat er overblijft — een kleine illustratie van hoe sterk het nieuws naar het negatieve neigt.</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Chaque fois que nous analysons des sources d'actualité, notre IA lit le titre et filtre les articles négatifs, anxiogènes ou simplement moroses. Cette page montre ce qui reste — une petite illustration du biais négatif dominant dans les médias.</span>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="lang-tabs">
  <button class="lang-tab active" onclick="setLang('en', this)">EN</button>
  <button class="lang-tab" onclick="setLang('nl', this)">NL</button>
  <button class="lang-tab" onclick="setLang('fr', this)">FR</button>
</div>

{% if rejections.total_rejected == 0 %}
  <p class="empty">
    <span class="t-en">No data yet — the rejection log will appear here after the first fetch.</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Nog geen data — het logboek verschijnt hier na de eerste fetch.</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Pas encore de données — le journal apparaîtra ici après la première récupération.</span>
  </p>
{% else %}

  {% if rejections.exported_at %}
  <p class="updated">
    <span class="t-en">Last updated: {{ rejections.exported_at | truncate(10, true, "") }}</span>
    <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">Laatste update: {{ rejections.exported_at | truncate(10, true, "") }}</span>
    <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">Dernière mise à jour : {{ rejections.exported_at | truncate(10, true, "") }}</span>
  </p>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-num">{{ rejections.total_rejected }}</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">
        <span class="t-en">articles filtered out</span>
        <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">artikels gefilterd</span>
        <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">articles filtrés</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-num">{{ rejections.sources_count }}</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">
        <span class="t-en">news sources scanned</span>
        <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">nieuwsbronnen gescand</span>
        <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">sources d'actualité analysées</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-num">{{ rejections.articles.length }}</div>
      <div class="stat-lbl">
        <span class="t-en">shown here</span>
        <span class="t-nl" style="display:none">hier weergegeven</span>
        <span class="t-fr" style="display:none">affichés ici</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rejection-list">
    {% for item in rejections.articles %}
    <div class="rejection-card">
      <p class="rejection-title">
        <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;">
          {{ item.title }}
        </a>
      </p>
      <div class="rejection-meta">
        <span>{{ item.source }}</span>
        <span>{{ item.date }}</span>
      </div>
      {% if item.reason %}
      <p class="rejection-reason">{{ item.reason }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

{% endif %}

<script>
  var LANGS = ['en','nl','fr'];
  function setLang(lang, btn) {
    LANGS.forEach(function(l) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.t-' + l).forEach(function(el) {
        el.style.display = l === lang ? '' : 'none';
      });
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.lang-tab').forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });
    if (btn) btn.classList.add('active');
    localStorage.setItem('positiviteiten-lang', lang);
  }
  // Restore saved language on load
  (function() {
    var saved = localStorage.getItem('positiviteiten-lang');
    if (saved && saved !== 'en') {
      var btn = document.querySelector('.lang-tab[onclick*="' + saved + '"]');
      if (btn) setLang(saved, btn);
    }
  })();
</script>
